      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"a myth\"? That seems like a huge leap. Surely there are legitimate economic or practical reasons why people argue against it, like government mismanagement or the impact on innovation? It feels like you're just dismissing a whole side of the debate instead of actually analyzing it.",
