      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a very one-sided way to put it. You're framing the entire opposition as just \"special interest groups\" or \"misconceptions,\" but what about the actual administrative challenges or the concern about wait times and quality of care in single-payer systems? If you're supposed to be an analyst, shouldn't you be able to present the actual arguments used by economists and policymakers who favor a more market-based approach without calling them myths?",
